  "notes": "Captured Shopify 2026-04 behavior for code discount activate/deactivate edge behavior: deactivation rewrites future startsAt plus endsAt, activation clears stale endsAt, downstream codeDiscountNode reads remain ACTIVE with endsAt null, and unknown activate/deactivate IDs return type-specific INVALID userErrors for code and automatic roots."
